interview_questions.user_template:
Generate practice interview questions for this candidate.

Job Description:
{job_description}

Candidate Profile:
{candidate_profile_summary}

Candidate Evaluation:
Strengths: {strengths}
Weaknesses: {weaknesses}

Respond with JSON:
{
  "questions": [
    {"id": "q1", "question": "Interview question", "category": "Behavioral|Technical|Situational|Weakness"},
    ...
  ]
}

Generate 10 questions:
- 4 behavioral questions (past experiences using STAR method)
- 3 technical questions (role-specific skills and tools)
- 2 situational questions (hypothetical scenarios)
- 1 question addressing a weakness from the evaluation

Make questions specific to this role and candidate background.
